              </CardDescription>
            </CardHeader>
            <CardContent>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-green-600">‚úÖ</span>
                  Skip to main content links
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-green-600">‚úÖ</span>
                  Focus trap for modals
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-green-600">‚úÖ</span>
                  Arrow key navigation
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-green-600">‚úÖ</span>
